[Text engl]
{Name}{}{none}
{Speech 1}{}{Predialogue installations}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{...}
{Speech 2}{}{You see a smooth wall, completely covered with names. If you look closely, beneath each name you can see a small inscription.}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Denergar}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Simms}
{Speech 2 Answer 5}{}{Groag}
{Speech 2 Answer 6}{}{Valizar}
{Speech 2 Answer 7}{}{Root}
{Speech 2 Answer 55}{}{[More]}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 3}{}{Brought the best people of the Wasteland together.}
{Speech 3 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 3 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 4}{}{There are two kinds of people: some have a rope around their neck, others shoot it off.}
{Speech 4 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 4 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 5}{}{The sharp drop in the radscorpion population is this man's doing.}
{Speech 5 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 5 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 6}{}{He used to say that potatoes boost reflex speed. Once I listened to him...}
{Speech 6 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 6 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 7}{}{Some say that during certain battles they saw this man in several copies at once.}
{Speech 7 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 7 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 8}{}{His machine gun worked just fine. As long as it didn't misfire...}
{Speech 8 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 8 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 9}{}{"Carnival - one of ours?"}
{Speech 9 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 9 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 10}{}{Went mad from making blacklists.}
{Speech 10 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 10 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 11}{}{He very rarely resorted to violence and believed that Jesus would by no means approve of violence, no matter what ends it was used for.}
{Speech 11 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 11 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 11 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 12}{}{"There are only seven of them, I'm getting wasted."}
{Speech 12 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 12 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 12 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 13}{}{An intellectual. Just don't tell him that.}
{Speech 13 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 13 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 14}{}{Don't try to read his name. You won't manage it.}
{Speech 14 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 14 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 14 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 15}{}{It's not the same without him...}
{Speech 15 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 15 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 15 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 16}{}{Dangerous. Beware.}
{Speech 16 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 16 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 16 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 17}{}{It's not the same without his jokes...}
{Speech 17 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 17 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 17 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 18}{}{His bazooka brought death... To everyone.}
{Speech 18 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 18 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 19}{}{"Time to shoot already?"}
{Speech 19 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 19 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 19 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 20}{}{And this one used to say that vodka boosts reaction speed... And I listened to him too...}
{Speech 20 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 20 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 20 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 21}{}{Zerker, if you're reading this, let us know.}
{Speech 21 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 21 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 21 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 22}{}{Got mixed up with the Chinese. Last saw him in San Francisco.}
{Speech 22 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 22 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 22 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 23}{}{If you love to argue but want to fall out of love with it, this is the man you need.}
{Speech 23 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 23 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 23 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 24}{}{A man of few words, but deadly dangerous.}
{Speech 24 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 24 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 24 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 25}{}{He talked smack. Verbally.}
{Speech 25 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 25 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 25 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 26}{}{Need a demolitions man? No, we won't give him to you. And yes, while I'm at it, I'd like to warn you about drafts.}
{Speech 26 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 26 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 26 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 28}{}{The Machine Spirit is somewhere near.}
{Speech 28 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 28 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 28 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 29}{}{He liked collecting explosives more than blowing anyone up.}
{Speech 29 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 29 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 29 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 30}{}{Just don't ask him about the Vampire...}
{Speech 30 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 30 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 30 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 31}{}{He raced across the Wasteland - by God.}
{Speech 31 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 31 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 31 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 32}{}{Serious.}
{Speech 32 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 32 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 32 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 33}{}{To the order to take off his APA, he replied only over his dead body. Dreams come true.}
{Speech 33 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 33 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 33 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 34}{}{Motorcycles were his passion. Though finding even one is quite a task.}
{Speech 34 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 34 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 34 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 35}{}{"If you wanna make some money - fuck yourself and make it funny"}
{Speech 35 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 35 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 35 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 36}{}{He knocked all the nonsense out of the Magister's head.}
{Speech 36 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 36 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 36 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 37}{}{Don't even think about touching this man's minigun with so much as a finger!}
{Speech 37 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 37 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 37 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 38}{}{Our beloved hamster! At least, that's what he used to say.}
{Speech 38 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 38 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 38 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 39}{}{If you find power armor - bring it to him, or he'll come for you.}
{Speech 39 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 39 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 39 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 40}{}{Our lady. The only one...}
{Speech 40 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 40 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 40 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 41}{}{He loved tomatoes and said they were very tasty. And I listened to him too...}
{Speech 41 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 41 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 41 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 42}{}{He liked to chop... and not just firewood. And yet, he remained the kindest man of all.}
{Speech 42 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 42 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 42 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 43}{}{He's d'Artagnan, lord of Klamath, and you're all - ...}
{Speech 43 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 43 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 43 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 44}{}{The best of the best. }
{Speech 44 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 44 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 44 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 45}{}{The terror of the BBN. Probably, after Fatal, even the Hubologists couldn't give the BBN folks back the eyes that got knocked out.}
{Speech 45 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 45 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 45 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 46}{}{Straight and steadfast. He'll get through anywhere. In a word - a tank.}
{Speech 46 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 46 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 46 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 47}{}{The growth in the centaur population is this man's doing... Or maybe not his hands...}
{Speech 47 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 47 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 47 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 48}{}{He shot magnificently.}
{Speech 48 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 48 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 48 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 49}{}{He liked being a melee fighter more.}
{Speech 49 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 49 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 49 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 50}{}{The only man who managed to pinch Fabias on the soft spot without any consequences for himself. Unless, of course, you count death as a consequence.}
{Speech 50 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 50 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 50 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 51}{}{A judge. Just don't tell him that.}
{Speech 51 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 51 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 51 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 52}{}{Although he was named after TNT, he preferred to turn his enemy into a sieve with his machine gun.}
{Speech 52 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 52 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 52 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 53}{}{He said he'd come back... We're waiting.}
{Speech 53 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 53 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 53 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 54}{}{Some consider him the best we ever lost... I'd like to believe it.}
{Speech 54 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 54 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 54 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
{Speech 27}{}{Always with a bazooka and hair. }
{Speech 27 Answer 2}{}{[Find another name]}
{Speech 27 Answer Back}{}{[Back]}
{Speech 27 Answer Exit}{}{[Exit]}
